此站在整個紐約地鐵有一個特徵，萊辛頓大道線和IND月台的轉乘只限南行方向，直至2012年9月末<ref name="nytimes1">[http://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/07/nyregion/07station.html?_r=1&scp=1&sq=with%20a%20connection%20to%20the%20no%206%20line&st=cse&oref=slogin With connection to No 6 line, a Manhattan transfer is coming] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/07/nyregion/07station.html?_r=1&scp=1&sq=with%20a%20connection%20to%20the%20no%206%20line&st=cse&oref=slogin |date=20150218192606 }} ''New York Times'' Retrieved August 2, 2006</ref>。下城IRT月台到IND月台的免費轉乘通道於IRT車站月台延長後的1957年5月19日啟用<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9B06E5D71631E63ABC4851DFB366838C649EDE|title=Passage Links Subways|access-date=October 10, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220132858/http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9B06E5D71631E63ABC4851DFB366838C649EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bleeckerbwaylafayette/>。這條單向轉乘存在了50年，由於IND往下城IRT月台的連接是純粹的巧合，而不是興建時就計劃的<ref name=bleeckerbwaylafayette>{{cite news |first=Sewell |last=Chan |authorlink=Sewell Chan |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/07/nyregion/07station.html |title=With Connection on No. 6 Line, a Manhattan Transfer Is Coming |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=May 7, 2005 |accessdate=April 27, 2011 |archive-date=2013-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130105204520/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/07/nyregion/07station.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。車站月台有較大距離導致1957年興建轉乘通道時不能在布利克街車站兩個月台興建。因此，北行月台不設免費轉乘，而轉乘需要向北步行一個街區到布利克街並額外支付車費，{{link-en|MetroCarod (紐約市)|MetroCard (New York City)|MetroCard}}持有者除外<ref name=nycta>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/The_New_York_Transit_Authority_in_the_1980s |title=The New York Transit Authority in the 1980s |accessdate=2017-01-30 |archive-date=2017-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906031353/http://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/The_New_York_Transit_Authority_in_the_1980s |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

IND月台和上城IRT月台的轉乘通道自1989年起開始規劃<ref name=nycta/>。然而直到2005－2009年[[大都會運輸署|大都會運輸署]]資金計劃分配5000萬美元以翻新複合，包括安裝[[美國殘疾人法案|無障礙通行]]升降機和興建往上城IRT月台的轉乘通道。重建以前，百老匯-拉法葉街車站只連接布利克街南行月台的極南端<ref name="nytimes1"/>。2012年3月26日，上城月台南移了300英呎到新興建的伸延段，而1950年代的北延同時關閉。同日，MTA宣佈往上城布利克街月台的轉乘通道會於6月末完工。

上城轉乘直至2012年9月25日方完全開放，而整個計劃的開支已經上升至1.35億美元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://mta.info/news/stories/?story=616 |title=Bleecker Street Platform Shifts |work=MTA.info |date=March 26, 2012 |accessdate=March 27, 2012 |archive-date=2012-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120817152316/http://www.mta.info/news/stories/?story=616 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同日，一條新的扶手電梯連接百老匯-拉法葉街車站的上城月台和新的轉乘夾層，並可連接至布利克街車站的上城月台。此外亦安裝了升降機以連接IND車站的不同月台和布利克街的月台<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ny1.com/content/top_stories/169624/transfers-at-bleecker-street-are-no-longer-a-bleak-situation |title=Transfers At Bleecker Street Are No Longer A Bleak Situation |work=[[NY1|NY1]] |first=Tina |last=Redwine |date=September 25, 2012 |accessdate=September 26, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130130082002/http://www.ny1.com/content/top_stories/169624/transfers-at-bleecker-street-are-no-longer-a-bleak-situation |archivedate=2013年1月30日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/09/24/nyregion/vexing-flaw-in-the-subway-is-finally-corrected.html |title=A Vexing Flaw in the Subway Is Finally Fixed |date=September 24, 2012 |author=Matt Flegenheimer |pages=A18–A19 |newspaper=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=September 28, 2012 |archive-date=2016-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007203910/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/09/24/nyregion/vexing-flaw-in-the-subway-is-finally-corrected.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wai.com/project.aspx?type=300&cat=320&id=1729 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015年10月28日 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813052825/http://www.wai.com/project.aspx?type=300&cat=320&id=1729 |archivedate=2016年8月13日 |df= }}</ref>。轉乘通道在IND車站以下加設了新的升降機和扶手電梯。街道層的升降機可直接到達南行IRT月台，而車站其餘四部升降機則連接各個IND月台和各個IRT月台<ref>{{cite news |url=http://new.mta.info/news/stories/?story=616 |title=Bleecker Street Platform Shifts |work=MTA.info |date=March 26, 2012 |accessdate=March 27, 2012 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>。
